name: NSURLHandle.Status
desc: These following constants are defined by NSURLHandle and are returned by status.

items.name: case notLoaded
items.desc: The resource data has not been loaded.

items.name: case loadSucceeded
items.desc: The resource data was successfully loaded.

items.name: case loadInProgress
items.desc: The resource data is in the process of loading.

items.name: case loadFailed
items.desc: The resource data failed to load.
